28:44.875 --> 28:59.087
what would you want it used for? I think I'd use it 
for scholarships, undergraduate, graduate

29:00.704 --> 29:08.523
scholarships for those students interested in 
theoretical geophysics. A million dollars is a

29:09.004 --> 29:12.834
lot of money, however. How would you identify the 
students? Who gets the scholarship? Well, it

29:17.545 --> 29:19.950
would depend on, first of all, their interest. 
