30:29.714 --> 30:35.002
been treated better. I think my contributions 
could have been recognized better. And the salary

30:43.861 --> 30:53.592
really wasn't very important, per se, because I 
got more money than I know what to do with now, even

30:43.861 --> 30:53.592
with the salary that I had, which wasn't very good. 
