30:54.893 --> 31:01.120
were getting salaries that were much more than 
mine. And I felt their contributions to the

31:01.460 --> 31:05.104
university weren't equal to mine. And that sort of 
bothered me more. I would rather they had cut the

31:07.587 --> 31:11.151
other guy's salary.

